    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏由一个人开发完成, 所以存在很多不足之处, 请指出这些缺点和有待改进的地方, 我会尽我所能完善游戏设计, 让它变得更好玩. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特别感谢Abdullah Konash分享的Arabic Support For Unity插件. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏指南</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(游戏项目所在的电脑不在身边，所以暂时无法修复游戏内容，恳请玩家们原谅，现将游戏指南公布，方便大家参考。)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局一：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集蜂去他国寻求外交援助，并将援助品送回本国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局二：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(简单关卡)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.筑巢蜂制作薄荷蜂王浆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.采集蜂将薄荷蜂王浆打包献给他国蜂王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.趁他国蜂王交配，战斗蜂进行冲击暗杀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4.我方蜂王吃下薄荷蜂王浆冒充他国蜂王……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局三：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全歼他国蜜蜂，并占领对方的蜂巢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结局四：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(普通关卡)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找四季之神(入口在三个石洞的下方)。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要三种献祭物品：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.薄荷蜂王浆：筑巢蜂制作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.阳光之蜜：采集蜂找向日葵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.月光之蜜：战斗蜂撞月光花。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏描述</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蜜蜂很忙是一款可以减轻生活压力的休闲养老小游戏, 扮演一只小蜜蜂, 然后构筑巢穴, 守卫家园, 收集花蜜, 贮藏蜂蜜, 争取度过冬天. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱的蜜蜂图形设计降低对昆虫的恐惧感.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7人合作游戏.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4+2种不同的职业和技能.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375090/extras/874f86270f95f5152f895c95fd7e1f04.avif?t=1757159785\" width=600 height=313 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获取食物和度过冬天的方式, 不止一种,  <br>探索和发现不同的玩法.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375090/extras/66684fc4e420ed0eda0ee63cb90f4635.poster.avif?t=1757159785\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375090/extras/66684fc4e420ed0eda0ee63cb90f4635.webm?t=1757159785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375090/extras/66684fc4e420ed0eda0ee63cb90f4635.mp4?t=1757159785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375090/extras/0ea9230250381a779f1767d475e93d83.poster.avif?t=1757159785\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375090/extras/0ea9230250381a779f1767d475e93d83.webm?t=1757159785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375090/extras/0ea9230250381a779f1767d475e93d83.mp4?t=1757159785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境温度会影响食物的消耗.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商人黄仙每天只卖3个东西.</p></li></ul>",
